  "texts": [
    "More complex systems with unknown initial states or longer developmental time scales can be captured faithfully through multiple experimental time points.",
    "To reconstruct the overall differentiation dynamics described by both across and within time points, we extend classical optimal transport (OT) 15, in particular WOT 15, with our RealTimeKernel to include within-time-point dynamics (Methods).",
